name: Cowboy Love is Pure 1-009: OBJECTIVE 1
description: Chapter 1, panel 9. A cowboy, having learned much from a guide, must summarise what has been learned and which instructions are to be followed. Love, the road, centipedes - all are entwined. To separate one element from the others is to misunderstand the whole. A comic by Little Old Man. This panel is an edition of 30.
